  "detailed_description": "<strong>Time Survivors</strong> is The Most Historically Inaccurate Roguelike Ever Made, where you can <strong>play as legendary historical characters</strong> like Abe Lincoln, Tesla, Cleopatra, and more, each now wielding unique custom abilities that revolutionize gameplay. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211390/extras/e29ef44726af23b56fe87f5eb867e63c.webp?t=1728313551\" width=610 height=45 /></span><br>Transform into a flying ninja robot as Oda Nobunaga, create defensive barriers made of cherry trees as Abe Lincoln (historically inaccurate™), or set the battlefield ablaze as Nero - the choice is yours. Each character brings<strong> a unique touch to every run</strong>, making each playthrough a unique adventure.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211390/extras/8fab3f7a41d30e949047f9d6f57af156.poster.avif?t=1728313551\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211390/extras/8fab3f7a41d30e949047f9d6f57af156.webm?t=1728313551\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Travel through time and <strong>fight hordes</strong> of memorable enemies as you unravel a mystery. With over 150 different weapons, items, Relics, and buffs to choose from, every run is a unique experience. Fight skeletons in the Medieval Age, Velociraptors and T-Rexes in the Stone Age, and discover plenty of quests and secrets along the way.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211390/extras/568fd7ae3f31f8547281a0a9dc2c6ae2.webp?t=1728313551\" width=610 height=45 /></span><br>But that's not all - Time Survivors presents a new meta progression system, allowing you to unlock and upgrade characters, weapons, and even <strong>game mode modifiers</strong>, using gold and other resources collected during your runs. Tailor your progression to your preferred playstyle and strategically <strong>allocate resources</strong> to create your own game-breaking build.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211390/extras/6e00ba7817b70e2fd4cc9192b20ba1a4.poster.avif?t=1728313551\" width=620 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211390/extras/6e00ba7817b70e2fd4cc9192b20ba1a4.webm?t=1728313551\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211390/extras/6e00ba7817b70e2fd4cc9192b20ba1a4.mp4?t=1728313551\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211390/extras/6b04eaad05448a709ae7731255a655a7.webp?t=1728313551\" width=610 height=45 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Play as epic historic characters, each with their unique ability<br></li><li>Historically inaccurate stages such as the Stone Age, the Dark Age, Ancient Egypt, and more full of enemies, secrets, mini bosses and end-stage boss<br></li><li>Skill-tree based meta progression for all elements in the game<br></li><li>Hundreds of different weapons, buffs, Cursed Relics, Powerups, and unlockables to choose from for a unique experience every run<br></li><li>Casual quick 20 minute play sessions + plenty of quests and secrets to discover<br></li><li>A Sandbox mode to test any overpowered build and train against any enemy</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211390/extras/f420ded95cbbf8b53f377e71e7a10909.poster.avif?t=1728313551\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211390/extras/f420ded95cbbf8b53f377e71e7a10909.webm?t=1728313551\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><br>And since you've come this far... Don't forget to wishlist and follow this page to stay up-to-date on the latest features and updates!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211390/extras/e95bb319e2b091396922b17f6a273a3f.poster.avif?t=1728313551\" width=612 height=92 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211390/extras/e95bb319e2b091396922b17f6a273a3f.webm?t=1728313551\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211390/extras/e95bb319e2b091396922b17f6a273a3f.mp4?t=1728313551\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
